&lt;Novamin Inc> said it received aproposed takeover offer from Breakwater Resources Ltd involvinga swap of one Breakwater share for two Novamin common shares.    It said the proposal also called for conversion ofoutstanding Novamin warrants into Breakwater common shares onthe same basis, provided the exercise price was paid by thewarrant holders.    Novamin, a mineral exploration company, said directorswould meet next Tuesday to deal with the proposal, which, itsaid, was subject to approval by Breakwater directors. Reuter&#3;